tvestergaard.fog.presentation

Class Parameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • tvestergaard.fog.presentation.Parameters

  • public class Parameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for validating types and converting the values of parameters in the provided HttpServletRequest.

      • isBoolean

        public boolean isBoolean(java.lang.String parameter)
        Checks that the value of the provided parameter can safely be extracted to a boolean value using the getBoolean(String) method.

        The values that can be converted to a boolean value are: - true -> true - on -> true - false -> false - off -> false

        Parameters:
        parameter - The name of the parameter to test the format of.
        Returns:
        true if the value of the provided parameter can safely be extracted to a boolean value using the getBoolean(String) method.

      • isEnum

        public <T extends java.lang.Enum<T>> boolean isEnum(java.lang.String parameter,
                                                    java.lang.Class<T> enumeration)
        Checks that the value of the provided parameter can safely be extracted to the type T using the getEnum(String, Class) method. The enum element is considered a match when the name of the enum element equals the value of the parameter.
        Type Parameters:
        T - The type of the enum type.
        Parameters:
        parameter - The name of the parameter to test the format of.
        enumeration - The EnumSet containing the legal values.
        Returns:
        true if the value of the provided parameter can safely be extracted to the type T using the getEnum(String, Class)

      • getEnum

        public <T extends java.lang.Enum<T>> T getEnum(java.lang.String parameter,
                                               java.lang.Class<T> enumeration)
        Extracts the T value of the provided parameter. The enum element is considered a match when the name of the enum element equals the value of the parameter.

        This method will not throw an exception when the isEnum(String, Class) method returns true for the same parameter name.

        Parameters:
        parameter - The name of the parameter to extract the double value from.
        enumeration - The enum.
        Returns:
        The double value of the value of the provided parameter.
        Throws:
        ParametersConversionException - When an error occurs while extracting the T value.
